@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gbwawh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.41 + wp.abs(tmp + 0.13)) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.76) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.17)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.13 / wp.sin(tmp + 0.06)))
    v1 = (v1 / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.92) - (v0 + 0.39 * tmp + 0.24)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v1)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
